function polynomialFromTheta(op,j){let a=[]; for(let d=0;d<=op.D;d++)a[d]=Number(opCoeff(op,j,d)); return a}
function polyTrim(c){c=c.slice(); while(c.length&&Math.abs(c.at(-1))<1e-10)c.pop(); return c}
function polyAddNum(a,b){let n=Math.max(a.length,b.length), c=Array(n).fill(0); for(let i=0;i<n;i++)c[i]=(a[i]||0)+(b[i]||0); return polyTrim(c)}
